Masiqale ngokucwangcisela iphulo elikhulu lokucoca izixeko zethu, iidolophu, iilokishi, iilali, izikolo size senze ntle yonke indawo yelizwe lethu.
Le nkqubo yemisebenzi ijolise ekwenzeni uMzantsi Afrika ube yindawo engcono yabantu bonke.
