Ngokuqonda amandla wezoqoqosho weNtshona Koloni noNxweme lwaseNtshona, simisele uMmandla woPhuhliso lwamaShishini i-Saldanha saze savula nemizi-mveliso emibini emitsha e-Atlantis.
