Mathandazwe nabahlobo,
Unyaka wama-2012 ngokhethekileyo kuba usekwaphawula isikhumbuzo se-16 soMgaqo-siseko weRiphabliki, obonisa ngokucacileyo iinjongo zethu ezifezekileyo zentando yesininzi.
