Ukususela ngowama-2009, ndityikitye izigunyaziso ezingama-34 eziyalela i-SIU ukuba iphande izityholo zorhwaphilizo, inkohliso okanye ulawulo olugwenxa kumasebe ngamasebe nakumaqumrhu karhulumente.
